sequenceDiagram
  actor User
  participant Frontend
  participant API
  participant DB
  User->>Frontend: Open categories page
  Frontend->>API: GET /categories with JWT
  API->>DB: Read tenant-scoped categories
  API-->>Frontend: Main categories and subcategories
  alt create main category
    User->>Frontend: Enter category name
    Frontend->>API: POST /categories without parentId
  else create subcategory
    User->>Frontend: Select parent and enter name
    Frontend->>API: POST /categories with parentId
  end
  API->>API: Validate Zod schema
  API->>DB: Insert tenant-scoped category
  API-->>Frontend: Created category
  Frontend->>API: GET /categories with JWT
  API-->>Frontend: Updated category library
